{"title":"钢铁长堤","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":8,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁长堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女娲修补的那一方天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然塌陷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天河决口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大暴雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，金黄的田野淹没在大水里了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，美丽的家园淹没在大水里了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运土，打桩，筑坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋战在暴雨里三天三夜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡堤，查漏，堵洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸泡在雨水里六天六夜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背老，抱幼，转移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔忙在洪水里九天九夜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万人拧成一股劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结成一道坚不可摧的钢铁长堤！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}